									<div class="post_tag"><i class="fa fa-tags"></i><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/africa/" rel="tag">Africa</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/an-encyclopedia-of-gardening-for-colored-children/" rel="tag">An Encyclopedia of Gardening for Colored Children</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/antigua/" rel="tag">Antigua</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/arawaks/" rel="tag">Arawaks</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/authors-guild/" rel="tag">Authors Guild</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/authors-guild-foundation/" rel="tag">Authors Guild Foundation</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/benjamin-west/" rel="tag">Benjamin West</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/botanical-gardens/" rel="tag">botanical gardens</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/botany/" rel="tag">Botany</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/british-empire/" rel="tag">British Empire</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/captain-cook/" rel="tag">Captain Cook</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/caribbean-literature/" rel="tag">Caribbean literature</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/caribbean-writers/" rel="tag">Caribbean writers</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/christopher-columbus/" rel="tag">Christopher Columbus</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/colonialism/" rel="tag">colonialism</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/flowers/" rel="tag">Flowers</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/gardening/" rel="tag">gardening</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/gardens/" rel="tag">gardens</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/greta-thunberg/" rel="tag">Greta Thunberg</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/jamaica/" rel="tag">Jamaica</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/jamaica-kincaid/" rel="tag">Jamaica Kincaid</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/julius-caesar/" rel="tag">Julius Caesar</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/kara-walker/" rel="tag">Kara Walker</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/mountaineering/" rel="tag">mountaineering</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/nature/" rel="tag">nature</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/plants/"